        "rich_text_tY7m9N": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "1st Para",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>With every weekend and party invitation, there’s a pressing question - \"What should I wear?\" Holidays are the perfect time to style yourself the way you have always dreamed of! Whether you are heading to a glamorous cocktail party, a cozy family or friends gathering, or a festive office bash, the right outfit can set the tone. Your outfit is complete only when styled with the perfect accessories - the right sling bag, the right party wear jewellery and the right footwear. With parties always being just around the corner, its time you check out online diamond jewellery and plan your next perfectly balanced outfit! </p>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
        },
        "rich_text_7Nnf8j": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "The Midnight Classic: Little Black Dress with a Twist",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>The Midnight Classic: Little Black Dress with a Twist</h2>",
            "custom_id": "midnight"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_jExVty": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/1_2a203ea3-0d2c-451f-9a5d-f086b5688cad.jpg",
            "text": "<p>No list of party outfits is complete without considering a little black dress. You can never go wrong with this classic outfit, with the power it exudes with its simplicity. Bring a little surprise to the outfit with the details. Think asymmetric sleeves or velvet accents. Every black dress begs for the right jewelry. Diamond <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/stud-earrings\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Stud Earrings\">stud earrings</a> and a <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/tennis-bracelets\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Tennis Bracelet\">tennis bracelet</a> bring an understated brilliance. </p>",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_9txWb4": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>If your neckline is bare, a solitaire jewellery pendant looks absolutely stunning. Pair with a pair of black strappy heels and you are ready to go! </p>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
        },
        "rich_text_qhnrEY": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Velvet Outfits - Luxe Comfort Text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Velvet Outfits - Luxe Comfort</h2>",
            "custom_id": "velvet"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_kcC6qx": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/2_826df336-2b52-4418-8010-e8e812572fd0.jpg",
            "text": "<p>Velvet whispers luxury. Its plush texture demands jewelry that doesn’t get hidden in the background. This is your chance to make the best of colored <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/lab-grown-diamond\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Lab Grown Diamonds\">Lab Grown Diamonds</a>. Picture trendy jewellery with a pop of color - like our <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/products/cotton-candy-hexdiamond-earrings\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Cotton Candy Hex Diamond Earrings\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">Cotton Candy Hex Diamond Earrings</span></a>.  With velvet dresses, less is more. You just need one statement piece that can strike the perfect balance and bring you the spotlight. </p>",
            "reverse_layout": true,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_pAdKDJ": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>To add a touch of glimmer that dances with your movements, choose a dainty tennis bracelet or a diamond <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/all-necklaces\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Necklace\">necklace</a> set. </p>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
        },
        "rich_text_KNFAhF": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Winter Whites - Understated Elegance",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Winter Whites - Understated Elegance</h2>",
            "custom_id": "winter"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_FUekT7": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/3_d1951020-b9c0-4b8d-ad68-6fcad5e8b038.jpg",
            "text": "<p>Choosing jewellery for her can be difficult during winters. Winter whites are a canvas of endless possibilities. A creamy knit dress carries an air of sophistication while providing comfort. Pair it with a diamond necklace for a subtle yet elegant look. You can even create a necklace earring set with matching huggies. </p>",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_ehJT3G": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Lady in Red",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Lady in Red</h2>",
            "custom_id": "red"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_z9MKAA": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/4_75b5d9bb-5e15-480e-975f-b290b720f2e8.jpg",
            "text": "<p>Make your presence known with red. May it be a cowl neck red dress or a red blazer, the color brings you to the spotlight. As the red radiates its elegance and power, think of jewellery that contrasts the shade. A gold jewellery necklace or a <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/solitaire-rings\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Solitaire Ring\">solitaire ring</a> strikes the balance without overpowering the look. If you are wearing a red sleeveless dress, go all out by layering bracelets such as a cuff bracelet and a tennis bracelet followed by a <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/chain-bracelets\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Chain Bracelet\">chain bracelet</a>. </p>",
            "reverse_layout": true,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_CdzdJy": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Sequins That Speak Before You Do",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Sequins That Speak Before You Do</h2>",
            "custom_id": "sequins"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_Rff3AD": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/5_08dbda34-01b5-41fc-833e-465065d4e715.jpg",
            "text": "<p>Bring refinement to your sequined outfit with jewellery that complements the dress, not competes. Sequined dresses command attention and require jewellery that quietly announces its elegance. A pair of elegant diamond studs works wonders. Style the dress with diamond rings that look minimal and dainty. Think of jewellery here as a quiet but essential sparkle that completes the look. </p>",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_ApaPCw": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Chic Jumpsuit",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Chic Jumpsuit</h2>",
            "custom_id": "jumpsuit"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_RtgBHH": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/6_72fc4291-95c2-4069-b889-2903a6f10afa.jpg",
            "text": "<p>A popular holiday outfit is a jumpsuit and reasonably so - it is comfortable, sleek and looks drop dead gorgeous while exuding confidence and power. This tailored yet playful outfit is a versatile holiday fit, and demands jewellery that looks equally chic. Explore the right combination of diamond jewellery to bring out this lasting impression. With jumpsuits,  earrings often become the hero of the outfit. </p>",
            "reverse_layout": true,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_X8CzgP": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Wear a pair of <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/sui-dhagas\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Sui Dhaga\">sui dhaga</a> earrings to make a statement and pair it with a ring design with a diamond equally elegant. </p>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
        },
        "rich_text_fApPij": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Festive Indian Party Wear",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Festive Indian Party Wear</h2>",
            "custom_id": "indian"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_mCALwr": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/7_e3615769-2d05-4f40-8aae-fde56ca281b7.jpg",
            "text": "<p>Ofcourse holidays aren’t just about Western wear. For many of us, holidays are woven with traditions, where sarees and lehengas take centre stage. Think Deepika Padukone in her iconic Yeh Jawaani Hai Deewani look and you know that’s a party outfit you would love to pull off! If the neckline is bare, a diamond <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/tennis-necklaces\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Tennis Necklace\">tennis necklace</a> will certainly earn a lot of compliments. Cocktail parties with an Indian twist demand jewellery <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/all-rings\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Rings\">rings</a>. Complete the look with jewellery <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/all-earrings\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Earrings\">earrings</a> with a shine that peeks through your hair and frames your face perfectly. </p>",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_iLcwtB": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Conclusion ",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Conclusion </h2><p>The beauty of holiday party dressing lies in the details. A deep V-neckline asks for a pendant, an off-shoulder begs for a choker, and a high neckline demands statement earrings. More than these styling tips, what matters is experimenting, such as layering or choosing Lab Grown Diamond jewellery which lets you create your dream look without a compromise. This season, let your look be more than just wearing an outfit, let it be unforgettable. </p>",
            "custom_id": "conclusion"
          }
        }
      },
